CO2e emissions in the use phase of our products During the use phase of our products, the main source of CO2e emissions is electricity consumption. This means that the key strategies for reducing emissions during the product use phase aim at increasing energy efficiency and promoting automation and digitalization.

Our strategic focus on energy efficiency, automation, and digitalization in industry, electrification, buildings, and transportation allows us to offer our customers products that are highly efficient, high-quality, and long-lasting. Our efficient electric motors are also an important factor in use- phase emissions.